{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to get up, I think, at 6 o'clock they came and woke us up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had work clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us work clothes, like overalls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did not have the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's another distinction from concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did not have those striped outfits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had regular work clothes-- might have been former air force overalls-- work-- work clothing from the air force that they had left and that they gave us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we started working every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no-- No, that's another distinction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, that was only in the regular concentration camps that you had-- So they did-- You know, we got up every morning-- There were a number of problems.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, they wouldn't give us enough food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the food was very limited.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, there was a mess hall where we would all march and get our rations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was never enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it was very-- we did not get-- we didn't share the food with the air force personnel, German air force personnel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had a special kitchen for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They made it pretty clear that, you know-- that-- that we are expected to do the work, and even if it's hard work, and not to complain about it, and do it-- because otherwise you're going to be sent to possibly to a more severe camp, you know?",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you knew about these more severe camps?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, we knew about the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That talk had become-- you know-- it was-- had become-- still, it was not-- wide-- I mean, it was not real widely known.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was a level of knowledge among people that nobody dared to really to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But everybody was whispering it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
